==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: hovercraft
<hw>hov"er*craft</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A vehicle that
rides over water or land supported by the pressure of a stream of air
generated by downward-thrusting fans, and is propelled forward by an air
propeller; also called <altname>ACV</altname> and <altname>air-cushioned
vehicle</altname>.</def> <mark>[Mostly found in Great
Britain]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hoverer</ent>⟦br⟧
